text: I ordered online and later wanted to cancel the order because they said THEY WOULD DELIVER IT IN 2 HOURS. So I couldn't cancel it online and tried to call them, they were not picking up for single 20-25 minutes. Absolutely hate the service.

name: SuperLady
text: Wish I could give a negative star! My pizza was 20 mins late, cold, and the driver argued with me about the directions to enter from a different street which were posted at the gate and included in my online instructions. Horrible horrible service!

text: Under baked every time, yes I came crawling back many times, but always under baked.

text: This place has horrible and rude management. Half of the specials pizza hut offers are not honored here. There people will rip you off and when you call to cancel and order they talk back and say that they will charge you anyways. This place sucks ass I can't wait until they go out if business.
